commit.message: Fix header include in gk_ms_inttypes.h
Added valgrind support
Added some valgrind-compatible cmake options (off by default)
Added gk_GetProcVmPeak() for getting the info from /proc/self/status
added binary read/write for char files
some minor cleaning up

Consistent declaration of functions and prototypes

Avoids errors of the kind:

getopt.c:770:5: error: conflicting types for 'gk_getopt'
  770 | int gk_getopt(int argc, char **argv, char *options)
      |     ^~~~~~~~~
In file included from GKlib.h:70,
                 from getopt.c:37:
gk_getopt.h:56:12: note: previous declaration of 'gk_getopt' was here
   56 | extern int gk_getopt(int __argc, char **argv, char *options);
      |            ^~~~~~~~~
mingw missing sys/resource.h
minor cleaning up
Added v3 by removing mallocs from v2
hmap-based unique
Added initial implementation of gkuniq
